<br>
Mages suck post 30 or so, unless they have their epic... then theyre a pain especially outdoors when their pet has velocity.<br>
<br>
I dont see why people think necros are so tough... pets can be rooted/snared pretty easily, can dispell a lot of their dots... can cure the rest and they have very low hp. Unless they can get you in a place where they can abuse Z axis and kite you they arent really a problem for me.<br>
<br>
Rogues vary depending on gear and skills... if you play them right they can kill anybody at 59 i can kill anybody except maybe a shadowknight if i make the first move.<br>
<br>
I kinda agree with everybodys opinion on druids, at least from a rogues perspective. Good dots, good nukes, dmg shield, heals... in tight places theyve been easy for me (velks, seb etc)<br>
<br>
I agree with Tsunamii on enchanters to an extent...&quot;anybody they can land nukes on they own&quot;. Cant land nukes on many people at high levels =) Id think theyd kill most casters at high levels because of mana drains....I killed an enchanter before she had a chance to get tash off recently =P<br>
<br>
Anyway... i could go on forever.<br>
